{B01: Scandinavian Defence} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qd6 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. Bc4
a6 6. h3 (6. d4 e6 7. Qe2 b5 8. Bd3 Bb7 9. O-O Be7 10. a4 b4 11. Ne4 Qd5 12.
Nxf6+ Bxf6 13. c4 bxc3 14. bxc3 O-O 15. Rb1 Bc6 16. c4 Qh5 17. Be4 Qg4 18. d5
exd5 19. cxd5 Re8 20. Rb4 Bxd5 {Crosa Coll,M (2384)-Giaccio,A (2517)
Montevideo 2002 1-0}) (6. d3 Nc6 7. a3 b5 8. Bb3 Bb7 9. Qe2 e6 10. Bg5 h6 11.
Be3 Be7 12. O-O Ne5 13. Nxe5 Qxe5 14. d4 Qf5 15. Rad1 Rd8 16. Qd3 Qh5 17. Bf4
c5 18. Nxb5 O-O 19. Nc3 Rxd4 20. Qe2 Rxf4 {Elistratov,S (2251)-Kozionov,K 
(2387) Voronezh 2014 0-1 (35)}) 6... b5 7. Bb3 Bb7 $146 (7... c5 8. d3 Bb7 9.
O-O e6 10. a4 b4 11. Ne2 Bxf3 12. gxf3 Nbd7 13. Bf4 Qc6 14. Kg2 h5 15. a5 Bd6
16. Ba4 Qc7 17. Qd2 Nd5 18. Bxd6 Qxd6 19. c4 Ne7 20. d4 Nf5 21. Rfd1 Nh4+ 22.
Kf1 {Ricaurte Lopez,J (2353)-Morejon Rodriguez,E (2173) Cali 2001 1-0}) 8. d3 {
Consolidates e4} e6 {Covers d5} 9. O-O Be7 10. Qe2 c5 11. a3 (11. Rd1 O-O $11)
11... Nc6 12. Ne4 {White threatens to win material: Ne4xd6} Qc7 13. a4 O-O 14.
axb5 axb5 15. Bg5 $2 (15. Rxa8 $142 {and White is still in the game} Rxa8 16.
c3 $15) 15... Nxe4 $19 16. Bxe7 Qxe7 17. dxe4 (17. Qxe4 Nd4 18. Qe3 Bxf3 19.
gxf3 Qf6 $19) 17... c4 $19 18. Bxc4 bxc4 19. Qxc4 (19. Rxa8 Bxa8 20. Qxc4 Qb4
$19) 19... Qb4 20. Qxb4 Nxb4 0-1

