(14. a4 b4 $11) 14... Rd8 (14... d4 15. a4 a6 16. e4 $11) 15. g5 {White
threatens to win material: g5xf6} Ne8 16. Qh5 {Black king safety dropped} (16.
a4 a6 $11) 16... g6 {Black threatens to win material: g6xh5} (16... c4 17. Be5
Bd6 18. bxc4 bxc4 19. Nf3 $15) 17. Qh4 (17. Qe2 c4 18. dxc4 dxc4 19. bxc4 Nd6
