Be5 Nd6 20. Qe1 $11) 19. Ne5 $14 {White threatens to win material: Ne5xc6} Rcd6
$2 (19... Nf5 $142 $5 {and Black can hope to survive} 20. Qh3 d4 21. Nxc6 Qxc6
22. exd4 cxd4 $11) 20. Ng4 $16 Nf5 $4 {the position was bad, and this mistake
simply hastens the end} (20... Ne8 $142 21. Be5 Qe7 $16) 21. Nf6+ (21. Nf6+ Kg7
