{B30: Sicilian: 2...Nc6 3 Bb5, lines without ...g6} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4
e6 4. c3 Nf6 $146 {Black threatens to win material: Nf6xe4} (4... d5 5. exd5
exd5 6. Qe2+ Be7 7. Bb5 Nf6 8. d4 O-O 9. h3 Bd6 10. O-O Re8 11. Qd1 Ne4 12.
