threatens to win material: Ne4xf2} 33. f3 {White threatens to win material:
f3xe4} (33. Rxb6+ Kc5 34. Rb8 Nxf2 $11) 33... Kc5 {Black threatens to win
material: Kc5xb5} 34. Bd3 {White threatens to win material: Bd3xe4} Nd6 35.
Bxh7 (35. Rh8 $5 $11) 35... Nc4+ $17 {Black forks: e3} 36. Kb3 (36. Ka2 Nxe3
37. g4 Nc4 $17) 36... Nxe3 37. g4 Nd5 (37... Nc4 $142 $5 38. Be4 b5 $17) 38.
