Nc8 $142 $14 {was much better}) 42. Rd5+ $18 Kc4 43. Rd3 (43. Rd1 $142 {
and White has triumphed} Kc5 44. Rc1+ Kd6 45. Bxc6 $18) 43... b4 $16 44. axb4
